types of microorganisms

00:04:43.529 --> 00:04:45.340
that are there, and
how they're interacting

00:04:45.340 --> 00:04:48.173
with the non-living things, the air.

00:04:48.173 --> 00:04:51.830
How they're interacting
with the oil on your skin,

