the major types of land ecosystems

00:05:16.060 --> 00:05:17.143
on our planet

00:05:18.668 --> 00:05:20.274
and where you might find them.

00:05:20.274 --> 00:05:22.991
And these different
types of land ecosystems,

00:05:22.991 --> 00:05:25.510
these are called biomes.

00:05:25.510 --> 00:05:26.613
Biomes.

