00:05:33.893 --> 00:05:36.064
You can find it in Southeast Asia.

00:05:36.064 --> 00:05:39.405
You can find it in
Central and even Southern

00:05:39.405 --> 00:05:41.046
or North America.

00:05:41.046 --> 00:05:43.030
You have boreal forests which you'll find

00:05:43.030 --> 00:05:44.423
